d 'HATEMICOINT': module to implement cointegration tests with two unknown regime shifts following the methodology of Hatemi-J (2008)
d
d   The hatemicoint package implements three residual-based tests
d for cointegration in the presence of two unknown structural
d breaks. The methodology extends the Gregory and Hansen (1996)
d framework to accommodate two regime shifts, where both the timing
d and location of the breaks are determined endogenously from the
d data.
d
d KW: unit root tests
d KW: structural breaks
d
d Requires: Stata version 14
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260206
d
d Author:   Merwan Roudane, NA
d Support: email  merwanroudane920@@gmail.com
d
f hatemicoint.ado
f hatemicoint.sthlp
f hatemicoint_examples.do
